sif3.common.ws
Class BaseResponse

java.lang.Object
  sif3.common.ws.BaseResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BulkOperationResponse, Response
public class BaseResponse
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This is a utility class. All HTTP responses (over REST or SOAP) have a number of fields set. This class encapsulates some of these common fields. It is not intended to be used on its own rather as a base to more concrete responses. This class is more of a super class.

Author:
Joerg Huber
